{"tid":1495962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護 ; 凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。","createTime":"2019-08-22T09:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T10:49:23.000Z","uid":289747,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a95ba7f811476297d85680b51b0f248626a694","tid":1495962,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 敵人反對勇武，我們就要擁護 ; 敵人擁護和理非，我們就要反對。反之亦然。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家好明顯就係慢慢逼使勇武退場，擁護和理非上場，咁樣只會步雨傘嘅後塵！2014年我哋輸啲乜，大家忘記了？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 敵人反對罷課罷工罷市，我們就要擁護。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋說好 : <span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n我哋說好 : 光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n我哋說好 : 寧為玉碎，不作瓦全！<br />\n我哋說好 : 立即普選，否則攬炒！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從古至今，沒有一個極權管治係只用&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;嘅方法去推翻的。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從古至今，&ldquo;勇武&rdquo;都係推翻一個極權管治嘅方法，而&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;係這種方法嘅助燃料。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武為這場抗爭執行義務，<br />\n和理非為這個義務履行權力。</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a286676c04ea992db286f7223b475bd126a0add","tid":1495962,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"擁抱和理非嘅光環，只會注定失敗！<br />\n勇武絕不退場！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇和合一！齊上齊落！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b39949f2967c33f20b55921420fab99bc1de2cb","tid":1495962,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:51:53.000Z","msg":"擁抱和理非嘅光環，只會注定失敗！<br />\n勇武絕不退場！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇和合一！齊上齊落！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de3d1566b61baf5de97d61bf18d8b7305f11922","tid":1495962,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}